Cowok itu aneh banget ya, udah secara fisik dan sejarah diuntungkan jadi pihak yang lebih “superior” di tatanan peradaban, masih aja urusan cewek mau ngapain dikritisi, dijadikan olok-olokan terus ngasih tau what we should and should’nt be doing.

She was surprised and she never told me to do anything again. Which is great. But I found that over the course of 8 years since my undergrad, she is most terrible person I have ever met.

Thats when I realized that by keep doing what she told, it makes me less and less superior. The next day when she told me to do her shit again, I told her that I am busy with mine, and I am doing my writing with American style, like it or not.

She kept coming told me all the alphabets in the beginning of a news title doesn’t have to be lowercased, another time, she told me there is should be an enter twice between the title and the news body. The next days, she told me to do her jobs.
One day an a$$hole came up to me and told me its “realise”, not “realize”. That time I was inferior so I changed it. Another day the same person told me its “1 dec” not “December 1st”

Pertanyaan yg paling sering ditanyain akhir2 ini: “kak kita ada bonus demografi, persaingan makin ketat, negara ga bisa proteksionis, kita harus gimana?” Jawabannya selalu sama: work your ass of. Jgn tergantung abang/kanda/kakak, be good yourself.
